entries.title: Glamorous brunette whose love affair with rogue MP who faked his own death rocked 1970s Britain
entries.description: Once, however, Sheila Buckley was the glamorous young brunette whose love affair with rogue MP and Communist traitor John Stonehouse scandalised British politics.

entries.title: Joe Biden got furious about reminders of Donald Trump in the White House
entries.description: A new book revealed Joe Biden was angry when he came across reminders of Donald Trump in the White House, including a $50,000 golf simulator.

entries.title: Will Rishi Skywalker fight the Election with honour - or try to zap Starmer with a sneaky tax trap?
entries.description: DAN HODGES: Rishi Sunak believes a New Year brings 'a new hope' - the title of a Star Wars movie of which he's a great fan.

entries.title: Whitehall departments lost 50 laptops and phones every WEEK last year
entries.description: MPs have demanded an urgent inquiry into a worrying increase in the number of electronic devices that have been mislaid or stolen from Government departments.
